description: Simpson Strong-Wall WSWH/WSWM typical details sheet (page 2). Contains WSWM model table, standard and wood floor base connections, top connections, back-to-back top connection, wall height adjustments, trim zone/allowable holes diagram, alternate garage front options, and rake wall detail. Includes installation notes.

Detail 4: Back-to-back top connection for double panel configuration
Detail 5: Top of wall height adjustments and rake wall detail
Detail 6: Installation notes and Simpson catalog references
Single story WSWM on concrete detail
Alternate WSWH garage front options (Option 1 and Option 2)
Trim zone and allowable holes diagram for Strong-Wall panels
